requirements:

1. centos version >=6
2. gcc version >=4.4
3. libraries:
    yum install libpng-devel mysql-devel openssl-devel ImageMagick-c++-devel hiredis-devel

4. boost 1.55.0
    unzip to /opt:
        /opt/boost_1_55_0
        /opt/boost -> boost_1_55_0/

5. install b2
    http://www.boost.org/boost-build2/doc/html/bbv2/installation.html

6. other linux commands
    mail - send email
    sox - convert audio format
    monit
    rsync

7. startup
    moon -d -c /etc/moon.conf

